        public java.lang.Boolean hasObstacle(double fromX,
                                     double toX,
                                     double fromY,
                                     double toY)
        lets you know if there's an obstacle in the current coordinate.
        参数:
        fromX - - x-axis of start point
        toX - - x-axis of end point
        fromY - - y-axis of start point
        toY - - y-axis of end point
        返回:
        true if has obstacle between two point, false if not
